Class WorldMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • WorldMap

  • public class WorldMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates world map using the tilemaps at "src/tilemaps/w/w/_underlay", "src/tilemaps/w/w/_overlay", "src/tilemaps/w/w/_actorlay" where x is the world number. the -1 flag in all layers means do nothing. the -2 flag in the over layer means add a barrier.
